title: Prospect Avenue at Hamilton Avenue, to , Brooklyn

text:
Hamilton Avenue (right), at its intersection with Prospect Ave. (left), viewing south. Hamilton Avenue culminates at Third Avenue, where the buildings are seen in the center of the view running from right to left across the roof of the gas station.

View: July 22, 1940
View 2: July 22, 1940

P. L. Sperr

view 2: Neg. No. A-1023

view 3: to N.E. corner of Hamilton and Prospect Avenues.
